Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Michael Weiss the zip code wizard
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yh5hm
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 14 Jun 1991
Michael Weiss' research into zip codes can determine the books you read, the car you drive and how you like your eggs in the morning. Alistair Cooke finds out how.